**Description**

Currently, running the world generation script leads to errors that prevent it from running. This relates to not being able to find files.

**Reproduce**

1. `mkdir -p ~/my_worlds/world_xacros` `mkdir -p ~/my_worlds/worlds`
2. `roslaunch vrx_gazebo generate_worlds.launch requested:=$HOME/vrx_ws/src/vrx/vrx_gazebo/worlds/yamls/dock_shallow.yaml world_xacro_target:=$HOME/my_worlds/world_xacros/ world_target:=$HOME/my_worlds/worlds/`

**Error**

```
xacro: in-order processing became default in ROS Melodic. You can drop the option.
No such file or directory: /home/tylerlum/vrx_ws/src/vrx/vrx_gazebo/worlds/xacros/light_buoy.xacro
when instantiating macro: include_all_xacros (/home/tylerlum/vrx_ws/src/vrx/vrx_gazebo/worlds/xacros/include_all_xacros.xacro)
in file: /home/tylerlum/my_worlds/world_xacros/worlds0.world.xacro
xacro: in-order processing became default in ROS Melodic. You can drop the option.
No such file or directory: /home/tylerlum/vrx_ws/src/vrx/vrx_gazebo/worlds/xacros/light_buoy.xacro
when instantiating macro: include_all_xacros (/home/tylerlum/vrx_ws/src/vrx/vrx_gazebo/worlds/xacros/include_all_xacros.xacro)
in file: /home/tylerlum/my_worlds/world_xacros/worlds1.world.xacro
```

```
➜  vrx_gazebo ls worlds/xacros 
dock.xacro                nav_challenge.xacro  sandisland_minus_scene.xacro  scene.xacro           usv_wind_plugin.xacro
include_all_xacros.xacro  perception.xacro     scan_and_dock.xacro           stationkeeping.xacro  wayfinding.xacro
```

Expected files

```
&lt;?xml version=&#34;1.0&#34;?&gt;
&lt;world xmlns:xacro=&#34;http://ros.org/wiki/xacro&#34;&gt;
  &lt;xacro:macro name=&#34;include_all_xacros&#34;&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/sandisland.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/sandisland_minus_scene.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/scene.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/nav_challenge.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/light_buoy.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/qualifying_pinger_transit_2016.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/dock_2016.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/dock_2018.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/scene_macro.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/usv_wind_plugin.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find wave_gazebo)/world_models/ocean_waves/model.xacro&#34;/&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/perception.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/stationkeeping.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/dock.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/scan_and_dock.xacro&#34; /&gt;
    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/wayfinding.xacro&#34; /&gt;
  &lt;/xacro:macro&gt;
&lt;/world&gt;
```

**Workaround**

```
diff -r 6a3fbf97e42a vrx_gazebo/worlds/xacros/include_all_xacros.xacro
--- a/vrx_gazebo/worlds/xacros/include_all_xacros.xacro Wed Aug 21 13:49:58 2019 -0600
+++ b/vrx_gazebo/worlds/xacros/include_all_xacros.xacro Wed Aug 21 14:25:51 2019 -0700
@@ -5,11 +5,11 @@
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/sandisland_minus_scene.xacro&#34; /&gt;
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/scene.xacro&#34; /&gt;
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/nav_challenge.xacro&#34; /&gt;
-    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/light_buoy.xacro&#34; /&gt;
+    &lt;!-- &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/light_buoy.xacro&#34; /&gt;
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/qualifying_pinger_transit_2016.xacro&#34; /&gt;
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/dock_2016.xacro&#34; /&gt;
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/dock_2018.xacro&#34; /&gt;
-    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/scene_macro.xacro&#34; /&gt;
+    &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/scene_macro.xacro&#34; /&gt; --&gt;
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/usv_wind_plugin.xacro&#34; /&gt;
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find wave_gazebo)/world_models/ocean_waves/model.xacro&#34;/&gt;
     &lt;xacro:include filename=&#34;$(find vrx_gazebo)/worlds/xacros/perception.xacro&#34; /&gt;
```
